eligibility.inclusivecriteria:
1. Residing for the length of the project in 1 of the 8 randomly assigned intervention villages; 
2. member of a fixed cohort (n=500) of people aged 5-60 years, who agree to participate in the study;
3. randomly selected from each intervention village;
4. physically and mentally competent to answer the interview questions;  and
5. consent to be included.
